oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Braided Channels
Collection
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: FitzSimons, Patricia
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Braided Channels Research Collection includes materials collected on Australia women, land and history in the Channel country. The collection is constructed from some 70 hours of oral history interviews with women from Australia’s Channel Country, together with archival film, transcripts, photos and music.
